The paper deals with steganography in IP telephony, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The method used in the paper involves transcoding, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the detection of steganography, which is related to system and network security (cs.SD) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
